name: Five Nights at Dog's
description:
This is a fangame of Five Nights at Freddy's or inspired on Five Nights at Freddy's.

Original game made by Scott Cawthon

                                                                     Story:

You was reading a newspaper, when you found a place hiring a night guard to work from 12 AM until 6 AM and you accepted it...

THE GAME IS NOT A VIRUS!!! IT'S A FALSE POSITIVE!!!!!!!
